---
title: "{{ title }}"
slug: "{{ slug }}"
date: {{ date }}
series: "{{ series }}"
chapter: "{{ chapter }}"
article_variant: "insight"
{% if tags %}
tags:
{% for tag in tags %}
  - "{{ tag }}"
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
tags: []
{% endif %}
draft: {{ draft | lower }}
description: "{{ description }}"
affiliate_ids:
  amazon: "{{ affiliate_ids.amazon }}"
  rakuten: "{{ affiliate_ids.rakuten }}"
{% if affiliate_ids.others %}
  others:
{% for other in affiliate_ids.others %}
    - name: "{{ other.name }}"
      url: "{{ other.url }}"
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
  others: []
{% endif %}
disclaimer: "{{ disclaimer }}"
{% if images %}
images:
{% for image in images %}
  - "{{ image }}"
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
images: []
{% endif %}
---
{{ intro }}

## 記事のアウトライン（検索意図ベース）
{% for block in outline %}
- **{{ block.heading }}**
  {% for bullet in block.bullets %}
  - {{ bullet }}
  {% endfor %}
{% endfor %}

{% if hero_image %}
![{{ hero_image.alt }}]({{ hero_image.url }})
<small>Photo by <a href="{{ hero_image.photographer_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ hero_image.photographer }}</a> on <a href="{{ hero_image.pexels_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pexels</a></small>
{% endif %}

## 着眼ポイント（ネタバレ無し）
{% for point in summary_points %}
- {{ point }}
{% endfor %}

## テーマ深掘り
{% for item in insight.themes %}
### {{ item.title }}
{{ item.detail }}
{% endfor %}

## キャラクター視点
{% for item in insight.characters %}
- **{{ item.name }}**: {{ item.focus }}
{% endfor %}

## FAQ
{% for item in faq %}
- **Q. {{ item.question }}**  
  A. {{ item.answer }}
{% endfor %}

## 参考リンク（すべて公式）
{% for link in reference_links %}
- [{{ link.label }}]({{ link.url }})
{% endfor %}

{% if reference_links %}
{% set official = official_link if official_link else reference_links[0] %}
{{ "{{< affbox title=\"" }}{{ official.label or "公式リンク" }}{{ "\" desc=\"公式情報はこちら\" url=\"" }}{{ official.url }}{{ "\" >}}" }}
{% endif %}
